@node what "What is DawnVideoPoker?"

@{b}What is DawnVideoPoker?@{ub}

It's a Video Poker Machine Simulator, with standard poker @{"rules" link rules},
found in many bars & casinos.
It includes a @{"'Double or Nothing'" link double} subgame that really makes VideoPoker
the game it is. In V2.0 i have also added a new feature; @{"ACES HIGH" link acehi}.


@{b}What's in it?@{ub}

* @{"Double feature" link double} (This is what VideoPoker is About!)
* @{"'ACES HIGH'" link acehi} Bonus feat. Collect all 4 ACES and QUADRUPLE profit. (V2.0)
* @{"Statistics" link stats}
* @{"HighScore List" link hiscore}
* @{"Virtual Cards" link virtcard} By time cards get worn & dirty.
* Sfx (V1.5)
* A Lot Of Love!

@endnode

@node sysreq "System Requirements"

1. An AMIGA. (Donno if it will run on a vanilla A500!?!)

2. DVP2 Doesn't support RTG so you might need scan-doubler, xtra
   monitor or respective hardware to display it.
   In fact i don't give a shit! It's YOU that's incompatible
   if you can't run it, NOT me!

3. Preferable PAL mode. There is a NTSC-dectection system that displays
   the screens in a little better positions. However the high-score screen
   will not be 100% visable in NTSC.

4. Basic knowledge of Poker.

5. Luck?...

@endnode

