@node use "Usage - How to play."

@{b}Usage - How to play.@{ub}

When you first start DVP2 you will face the @{"Log-in" link login} promt.
This works both as a simple name entry and as @{"Prefs" link login} control.

Once you've entered your prefs (or cheats) and name, the game starts.

As default you are given $100 to play with.

The first thing you do is to decide how much to bet $1 to $5. $5 is
deafult. If you reach $150 you can bet $10.

Then press the 'DEAL' button. Five cards will be dealt.
The @{"Win/Hold lights" link winhold} will now indicate any winning combinations or in some
cases suggest wich cards to hold (green lights). If you are happy with this
choice; press RIGHT MOUSE-BUTTON to auto-select these cards, otherwise click
on the cards you wish to discard. Click on 'DEAL' once more and new cards
will be dealt to replace the ones you discarded. Now you either have a
winning hand according to the @{"Pay-off Rules" link rules}, or have lost your bet.
If you have won you have the choice to play the @{"Double game" link double}.

You will notice that all ACES in your final hands will be collected
at the left-side screen. This is a new bonus feature called @{"ACES HIGH" link acehi}.

Buttons:
* CASH OUT - Quit/Restart option screen:
                                       |
              CASH OUT - Quits, writes any high-scores.
              RESTART  - Log-In prompt. Deletes current game.
              CONTINUE - Resume current game.

* HIGH-SCORE - High-Score screen: (Note on @{"High-Scores" link hiscore})
                              |
              Click on left-side screen to view resp. statistics.

* STATS    - @{"Statistics screen:" link stats}
                              |
              Displays your current game statistics.

* BET      - Change your bet $1-5 ($10 if CASH>=$150).
* DEAL     - New hand/Change cards.
* DOUBLE   - @{"Double game" link double}

@endnode

@node login "Log-In Commands"

@{b}Log-In Commands:@{ub}

SPEED1 - Normal dealing speed.
SPEED2 - Faster dealing.
SPEED3 - Really Fast, Really.
SPEED0 - Slower dealing. (default of earlier versions)

(the 'speed' commands also accelerates button-delays etc.)

CARD1...5 - Replaces 'Card-top-image' with any of the five
            cards in GFX/CARDS. Feel free to @{"design your own cards" link designcard}.

RESET - Resets any cash related cheats you may have entered.

HI-RESET - Resets High-Score list.

NOSORT - Turns OFF Auto-Sorting (and 'Win/Hold lamps'), 'SORT' re-activates.

BASIC - Turns OFF ACES HIGH = standard videopoker. 'ACESHIGH' re-activates.

SHADE - Activates @{"advanced card-shading" link shade} (060 default). 'NOSHADE' deactivates.

H - These help instructions.

There are many other cheats & gags...give me a mail with feedback
and i'll send you some of the 'secret codes'.

@endnode

